title: dark electro-VA-Halotan Records Sampler 07 industrial aggrotech
description:
Artist: VA
Album: Halotan Records Sampler 07 (2013)
Genre: Dark Electro, Aggrotech, Electro-Industrial, EBM
Label: Halotan Records
Quality: 320kbps mp3
More info: www.halotan.net

Sampler 07 contains very dangerous dose of dark electro, industrial and aggrotech music. The style is modern and dancefloor-oriented while it retains a lot of aggressiveness.

It is very likely that you have already heard about most of the bands featuring on this release, so Sampler 07 is a good occasion to check out what they have been up to recently.
